## Changelog
### Features
* 13deaf6b2f0096314b7bbd03e485397414004c5d feat: Add --override-data-file flag
* 9df5bfa79c4fea7bdbd9f4cb4076da9474d0db7d feat: Add --override-data flag
* e9546b6463b389a19628fd22c4938a6ad3acf313 feat: Add --less-interactive to only prompt for conflicts
* 271bb75f1af15b50ee4eb9f1d5221e202c8ae3e3 feat: Add exec template function
* 5947399d827ada1f5065a5d3037b9282838d1ef1 feat: Group commands in help
### Fixes
* 63f39472f0cee7099c7fc54eb07f9fa6d79336e9 fix: Reverse command check for current user in docker feature
* 0cfd139f16b671f64ba6d1d8bee8730d36476bae fix: Report an error when --follow and --recursive are combined for directories
* ce44e944ea8de64a10c6d32876b97624a1d07810 fix: Fix value of Windows version environment variables
* fa4999d66f2f5b5b3c5307350c8b088892964e44 fix: Add destroy and ssh command descriptions to help
### Documentation
* ca59697196e4d86b166e273ae6af28c21681cd4d docs: Add link to article
* 2c439175be2c64132a3d36bf60b2d2947a947aca docs: Add link to chezmoi_modify_manager article
